Piper Burp Exension 
  Executes anything within Burp Suite (Interpeters, CLI and GUI tools...)

Sample Use Cases:
  Display JSON data using gron
    gron is a command line tool for grepping JSON
  Open a PDF file using Okular
    Okular is a universal document viewer
  Compare messages using diff or meld
    diff is a file compare tool
    meld is a GUI tool for comparing files and directories
  Uniquely identify bodies using md5sum
  Detect JWT-authenticate requests using grep
  Bypass WAF by modifying Scanner payloads using sed

